{
  "stem": "20035.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, that was probably the-- the-- the-- the most difficult part of-- of Birkenau to-- to be able-- to be next door to-- to be next to that [GERMAN] camp, to-- to see what can be done.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and once again, you know, the only separation is six, seven, or eight-foot area in between the wires.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally, sometimes in-- in the month of August.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Suddenly we were pushed on a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the way, that's the first time we went in a passenger train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had no idea where we are going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that train went on for-- and again, two or three days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And finally, we arrived to a-- in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We new that we are heading and we passed on near Berlin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, well, geographic, we knew enough where we are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we are just north of Berlin, northeast of Berlin, to a city which called Braunschweig if you want to spell, it's B-R-A-U-N-S-C-H-W-E-I-G.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Braunschweig is a comparatively large town where they had Bussing [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Bussing truck manufacturing plant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Bussing is B-U-S-S-I-N-G.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Bussing, to the best of my knowledge, was or is a division of Mercedes Benz Truck Division.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there we-- the train stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And probably a mile from the train station, they had a big camp, big, big camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Labor camp.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was strictly labor camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This was not an extermination camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was no Final Solution or extermination here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was death by-- by-- by labor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This camp, to compare to Birkenau, was a luxury camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because we had triple-decker bunks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It didn't mean that you slept in a bank-- or in a bunk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was eight people, I mean, in a row, on a wooden plank.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
